<li>Stroud, B. (1977). Hume, Routledge, London &amp; New York. (Complete study of Hume's work parting from the interpretation of Hume's naturalistic philosophical programme).</li>
<li>Hesselberg, A. Kenneth (1961). Hume, Natural Law and Justice. Duquesne Review</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Gilles_Deleuze" title="Gilles Deleuze">Gilles Deleuze</a>, <i>Empirisme et subjectivité. Essai sur la Nature Humaine selon Hume</i> (Paris: Presses Universitaires de France, 1953) trans. <i>Empiricism and Subjectivity</i> (New York: Columbia University Press, 1991)</li>
</ul>
